metadata.name: Birdies #1
metadata.description:
The Birdies Genesis are a new community based project of 50 really high flying birds that are nesting on the Ethereum Branch.

Being that this is a community based project we want to do more for the holders of the project, but we do plan on more charitable events. Giveaways, Whitelists, and etc. for joining our really cool club before we soar to the metaverse, and beyond.
